      • setEftCode

        public void setEftCode​(String eftCode)
        Set the Product EFT code.

        When using payment card with restricted use (e.g. fuel cards) the product code is used to determine eligibility for payment.

        The actual product EFT codes will be dependent on the country of operation and the acquirer in use.
